title: Full Show (Cowboys beat Giants, Westbrook on future in LA, KD on building championship culture)
description:
00:00 Cowboys take down undefeated Giants 23-16 on MNF
23:52 Westbrook on whether the Lakers want him in LA or not
58:50 Is CeeDee Lamb a top receiver after one-handed touchdown against Giants?
1:11:15 Is LeBron the GOAT if he passes Kareem this season?
1:23:12 Micah Parsons tweets “New Era” after Cowboys get 5 sacks and a win over the Giants on MNF
1:32:16 KD talks about wanting to build a championship culture during Nets media day.
1:43:11 Cowboys are one game behind the Eagles for the NFC East crown. Can Dallas win the division?
1:50:32 LeBron hypes up Saquon on Twitter. Demarcus Lawrence responds
1:54:45 Tyreek Hill trash talks Eli Apple ahead of Dolphins vs Bengals on TNF
